</div>
<div id="outline-container-org75bf18c" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org75bf18c"><span class="section-number-3">22.3.</span> Ex-dividend day                      T+1        (excluding dividend i.e. price of stock = stock price - dividend)</h3>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6c41810" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6c41810"><span class="section-number-3">22.4.</span> settlement day or Record day         T+2</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-22-4">
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org08632e9" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org08632e9"><span class="section-number-2">23.</span> size</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-23">
<p>
0.0001-0.0999: 10,000 shares
0.10-0.1999: 5,000 shares
0.20-0.5099: 2,500 shares
0.51-0.9999: 1,000 shares
1.00-174.99: 100 shares
175.00+: 1 share
</p>

<p>
10000 * .0001 / 0.0001  1/10000
5000  * 0.1   / 0.1     1/10
2500  * 0.2   / 0.2     1/5
1000  * 0.5   / 0.5     1/2
100   * 1     / 1       1
1
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org9ced2b6" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org9ced2b6"><span class="section-number-2">24.</span> halts</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-24">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4edb872" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4edb872"><span class="section-number-3">24.1.</span> market wide</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-24-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org500396c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org500396c"><span class="section-number-4">24.1.1.</span> SEC market disruptions.</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-1-1">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Up to 90 days (approval with notice to President).</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc993571" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc993571"><span class="section-number-4">24.1.2.</span> circuit break on decline of S&amp;P (i.e. Index):</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-1-2">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org40876d9"></a>7%  (9.30-3.25): 15 minutes         (MM can enter quotes and customer can order quotes to BDs during last 5 min)<br /></li>
<li><a id="org59c99be"></a>13% (9.30-3.25): 15 minutes         (MM can enter quotes and customer can order quotes to BDs during last 5 min)<br /></li>
<li><a id="org011795d"></a>20% (9.30-4.00): rest of the day<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7d648db" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org7d648db"><span class="section-number-3">24.2.</span> single stock</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-24-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1989ae2" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org1989ae2"><span class="section-number-4">24.2.1.</span> Exchange</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-2-1">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org335226d"></a>T1 pending news                                      (BDs can submit order to NASDAQ during this time.)<br /></li>
<li><a id="org680ccfb"></a>T2 release news                                      (BDs can submit order to NASDAQ during this time.)<br /></li>
<li><a id="org73f7c33"></a>T3 let new disseminate for 5 minutes and reopen<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org010f538" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org010f538"><span class="section-number-4">24.2.2.</span> SEC (NMS or OTC)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-2-2">
<p>
10 days for investor protection or market manipulation
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga21bb5f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orga21bb5f"><span class="section-number-4">24.2.3.</span> FINRA (NMS or OTC)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-2-3">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org2dcab13"></a>Halt on system error/pending news/halt in a associative security<br /></li>
<li><a id="org8c679b7"></a>SEC directed to halt.<br /></li>
<li><a id="org4708e3b"></a>10 days halt in extra ordinary situations.<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org2c2b300" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org2c2b300"><span class="section-number-3">24.3.</span> ADR</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-24-3">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8e261c0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org8e261c0"><span class="section-number-4">24.3.1.</span> foreign company halts due to pending news or some event</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-3-1">
<p>
Halt trading
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org27f8269" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org27f8269"><span class="section-number-4">24.3.2.</span> Foreign company halts due to regulatory reasons.</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-24-3-2">
<p>
No halt
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org34a5793" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org34a5793"><span class="section-number-2">25.</span> Close out /settlement</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-25">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1d52a53" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org1d52a53"><span class="section-number-3">25.1.</span> Short Sale : T + 3  (before open)</h3>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc68630c" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgc68630c"><span class="section-number-3">25.2.</span> Long Sale  : T + 5  (before open)</h3>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb50ebc1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgb50ebc1"><span class="section-number-3">25.3.</span> Threshold  : T + 14 (before open)</h3>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org6af3cc9" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org6af3cc9"><span class="section-number-2">26.</span> Risk Control</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-26">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7c31141" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org7c31141"><span class="section-number-3">26.1.</span> Pre-Trade Control: Automated control for automated trading system.</h3>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0d51276" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org0d51276"><span class="section-number-3">26.2.</span> If BD provides DMA: The control should be direct and exclusive (no out sourcing allowed)</h3>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org019427b" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org019427b"><span class="section-number-2">27.</span> Limit Up Limit Down</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-27">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0790b5c" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org0790b5c"><span class="section-number-3">27.1.</span> Band/LULD: is % above and below the stock reference price</h3>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org83400ff" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org83400ff"><span class="section-number-3">27.2.</span> Reference price: 5 minute average moving price of an stock which is</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-27-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgdc81440" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgdc81440"><span class="section-number-4">27.2.1.</span> calculated every 30 seconds.</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgde34200" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgde34200"><span class="section-number-4">27.2.2.</span> updated after 1% or greater change in the prior reference price.</h4>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga45611d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga45611d"><span class="section-number-3">27.3.</span> IF greater than 5% Limit then</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-27-3">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org82c12e1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org82c12e1"><span class="section-number-4">27.3.1.</span> price is changed to the limit</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-27-3-1">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org8676230"></a>IF == 5% Limit<br />
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org48acf27"></a>wait for 15 seconds<br /></li>
<li><a id="org70707e5"></a>During wait orders can be entered but they will not be executed.<br /></li>
<li><a id="org5f359ee"></a>IF the quote is not removed or executed within 15 seconds<br />
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="orgb9cd93f"></a>pause and wait for 5 minutes<br /></li>
<li><a id="org65888fd"></a>IF the quote is not removed or executed within 5 minutes<br />
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org94d91bc"></a>Primary Exchange can either pause or resume<br /></li>
<li><a id="orgcecedc4"></a>IF the quote is not removed or executed after 2nd halt<br />
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org3035372"></a>Each exchange (there decision) may either wait for 10 minutes and result.<br /></li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li><a id="orge4d5beb"></a>ELSE<br />
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="orgdaa1578"></a>EITHER order get canceled by the MM/BD/Customer<br /></li>
<li><a id="orgbd49426"></a>OR     order is executed<br /></li>
<li><a id="org974f76b"></a>Trading will continue<br />
<div class="outline-text-7" id="text-27-3-1-1-4-3">

<div id="org5e726a4" class="figure">
<p><img src="./LULD.png" alt="LULD.png" />
</p>
</div>
</div>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgcab72d4" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgcab72d4"><span class="section-number-2">28.</span> Short Sell</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-28">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgb92d1cd" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgb92d1cd"><span class="section-number-3">28.1.</span> Broker Dealer</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-28-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org67c6235" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org67c6235"><span class="section-number-4">28.1.1.</span> Locate</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-28-1-1">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org53021dd"></a>Agreement with institutional investors<br />
<div class="outline-text-5" id="text-28-1-1-1">
<p>
or
</p>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id="orgc53aa44"></a>Have availability<br />
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="orgf111141"></a>Should publish the list of available list and update every 24 hours.<br /></li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org3d7678c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org3d7678c"><span class="section-number-4">28.1.2.</span> Aggregate the position</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-28-1-2">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="orgcfad422"></a>real time<br /></li>
<li><a id="orgf681b96"></a>Avoid real time by independent unit aggregation; every unit / Trader will aggregate and will work independently for a specific unit (not more than one unit)<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgc871e8a" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc871e8a"><span class="section-number-4">28.1.3.</span> Reporting</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-28-1-3">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org70d9155"></a>every 15 days<br /></li>
<li><a id="org49155dc"></a>due 2 days ( 15 + 2 )<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf9375dc" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgf9375dc"><span class="section-number-3">28.2.</span> Restrictions</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-28-2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org08014a1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org08014a1"><span class="section-number-4">28.2.1.</span> IF market goes down by 10% or more.</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-28-2-1">
</div>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a id="org870b2db"></a>SS is restricted.<br /></li>
<li><a id="orgdda8047"></a>trade halt for that day and next day<br /></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8a2bed6" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org8a2bed6"><span class="section-number-3">28.3.</span> Restriction exceptions</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-28-3">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org94e4066" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org94e4066"><span class="section-number-4">28.3.1.</span> If the if price  higher than the NBB  (e.g. NBB 75.25-50 =&gt; SS 75.26) .</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd3a27fd" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgd3a27fd"><span class="section-number-4">28.3.2.</span> if long</h4>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd5fe05d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgd5fe05d"><span class="section-number-4">28.3.3.</span> If odd lot/warrant/right/covertible/vwap/riskless principal trade/recently traded and will settle next day.</h4>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgcc3e40b" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgcc3e40b"><span class="section-number-3">28.4.</span> In-Kind services</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-28-4">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org70ff1a8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org70ff1a8"><span class="section-number-4">28.4.1.</span> BD should</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-28-4-1">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>adhere order protection rule</li>
<li>best execution mandate</li>
<li>disclose any payments for order flow to affected customers.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
