<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">shares, then the position is in an</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">such as</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">open-fail state.</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">naked short selling,</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">can lead to</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">legal and regulatory consequences,</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">including</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">fines and penalties,</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">as well as</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">criminal charges and</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">imprisonment.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgb79a4e0" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgb79a4e0"><span class="section-number-2">39.</span> Short Sell</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-39">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd7420db" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgd7420db"><span class="section-number-3">39.1.</span> Circuit Breaker Rules</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-39-1">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org31f93cb" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org31f93cb"><span class="section-number-4">39.1.1.</span> Table summarizing the Designated Percentage requirements for different types of stocks and exchanges:</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-39-1-1">
