</div>
<div id="outline-container-org00f46f6" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org00f46f6"><span class="section-number-4">71.12.1.</span> Answer: Regulation M has a number of implications for investors. First, investors can be confident that the market price of securities is not being artificially inflated during a distribution. Second, investors can be aware of the exceptions to the rules of Regulation M. Third, investors can be aware of the penalties for violating Regulation M.</h4>
</div>
